name: Two Identical
description:
The best game for attentiveness and speed of decisions. Time is limited, hurry up to find all pairs of pictures. Collect them all and complete the levels, one by one. Relaxing game for true connoisseurs!

Two Identical - Find a pair game, each picture has its own copy, and you need to find it quickly. Difficulty levels will not let you get bored. Develop yourself and train your memory.

Game Features:
- Over 30 levels
- Memory Training
- Pleasant musical accompaniment
-Pixel Art
